Text.string: Looks like we need some better fighters!
You won't get away with that!
Bad Vault Thief! BAD, BAD VAULT THIEF!
Stop it, stop it, stop it!
We'll get you for that, rakk-stain!
Get out, get out, get out!
Come on, Scrapper, get that grunt!
I'm not afraid of you, witch!
Kill the witch! Drink the blood!
Nice pet! Looks like dinner to me!
Got your tickets to the cannon show?
Don't hate me because I'm beautiful!
Come out, come out wherever you are!
I'll find ya, crunch ya and soup ya!
We're more than you can handle!
You are a pimple on the ass of life!
I'll squeeze this rat until it pops!
Get a kill or don't come back!
Learn to fly or die die die!
Get out there and kill! Kill! KILL!
Come back a winner or not at all!
You could say I've got balls of steel!
Not recommended by ten out of ten dentists!
Takin' you down to junk town!
I know you're out there somewhere!
I'll just eat that thing too!
What you been feedin' that thing?
Reminds me of my third husband!
Wish my boys would grow like that!
Where'd all that beef come from?
You suck and your pet sucks!
Pick on someone your own size! ME!
Well if it isn't the milkman...
Ohhhh, my prayers have been answered.
They better not poop on me!
Not the face! Not my BEAUTIFUL face!
Suck hot ass, you rakk bastards!
Get it away! Get it AWAY!
Looks like some scrap for us!
Keep that pest away from me!
Wonder if we can trash it?
That doesn't look good for us.
Get up, you fools! Fight! FIGHT!
You were weak! I am strong!
No! I kinda liked that one!
Nobody else is allowed to die! Got it?!
Don't squirm. I'll chop you up!
Now lick my boots, you rat!
How do I smell from down there?
That's what happens to naughty heretics!
Feel the fury of the family!
We'll meet again... in the Great Vault...
Don't cry for me! Kill for me!
Should have used them... as bullet shields.
I died doin' what I love... killing...
At least I died young and beautiful!
I had... so much to live for...
At least... I outlived... most of them...
Make sure they pay for this...
I guess I like it, huh?
Suck it down! SUCK IT DOWN!
Guess I AM full of hot air!
Make me the happiest woman on Pandora, AND DIE!
Gonna stomp all over your corpse!
We fight for the Twin Gods!
Looks like we're makin' stew tonight!
Come on, come on! Come at me!
Gather round, family! It's feedin' time!
Bring it in! Bring it in! Finish 'em!
Come on, come on! Come on! Get the meat!
You're goin' in the dirt, Vault Thief!
I'm gonna blow your ass off your spine!
The family's gonna rip you APART!
Come on, get out here and fight!
Where are all my brothers and sisters?
Am I the only one left who ain't scared!
Somebody help me squish these rats!
Anyone with a gun should be out here now!
Quit chewing your toenails and fight!
Finally! Where the hell were you?
Show 'em what the family can do!
Go on with your bad self!
You so bad! But like, good-bad!
Killers get the good gruel tonight!
This'll knock the stink off ya!
Gonna have to mop you up!
What? You don't think I have more?
No! He was my second favorite!
Looks like I need a new Scrapper!
There's more where he came from!
Let's show them what we've got!
We're a force to be reckoned with!
Cannons and Scrappers, what more does a girl need?
You're worth less than a skaglick to me!
You're gonna get chopped! [beat; to self] Is that what the kids say?
Knew it would end this way!
